    <div class="content"><p>I think that interpretation would have required an entirely different <a href="http://www.youtube.com/glenra#p/a/u/1/vJcAoBAfLFY" rel="nofollow">parody song</a>.</p>
<p>It's a pity there are more Avatar movies on the way. As with _The Matrix_, not saying too much in a first movie gives viewers latitude to come up with their own interpretations that might beat what the filmmakers had in mind or are likely to come up with later when they need to extend the franchise.</p>
